ZH: 我估摸着明天会下雨。
EN: I estimate that it will rain tomorrow.

ZH: 我估摸着他今天会来。
EN: I reckon he will come today.

ZH: 估摸这个袋子里有五十个苹果。
EN: I estimate that there are fifty apples in this bag.

ZH: 估摸这个电影的票房会很高。
EN: It is estimated that this movie will have high box office numbers.

ZH: 你能估摸一下这个公路的长短吗？
EN: Can you estimate the length of this road?

ZH: 我估摸他明年就能毕业了。
EN: I reckon he will graduate next year.

ZH: 估摸今天有多少人会来参加会议？
EN: How many people do you estimate will come to the meeting today?

