EN: It is estimated that the price of this hotel room is around 100 dollars.

ZH: 你能估摸一下这栋建筑物的高度吗？
EN: Can you estimate the height of this building?

ZH: 我估摸他们的公司今年会有很大的发展。
EN: I estimate that their company will have significant growth this year.

ZH: 估摸这个项目需要多长时间才能完成？
EN: How long do you estimate it will take to complete this project?

